2. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a method to reject out-of-distribution samples using feature activations of intermediate layers as descriptors, which is a machine learning technique. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses a deep learning model to detect emphysema in chest x-rays, which is an application of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with the analysis of medical images (chest x-rays), which can be considered as a form of multimedia. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper uses a neural network (ResNet-50) for the analysis of chest x-rays, which falls under the domain of neural computing.
